      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "The Evil Star from Beyond",
        "Client": "Scarred Old Woman",
        "Description": "The Valstrax has returned. If\r\nyou plan on takin\u0027 it on, beware\r\nits wings! If they don\u0027t burn you\r\nto a crisp, they\u0027ll dang sure poke\r\nyou full of holes. Be quick and\r\nstay on your toes out there!\r\nGot it? Well, good luck to ya!",
